sourcesContent: import React from "react" import styled from "styled-components" import { Menu, Button } from "antd" import { Link } from "react-router-dom" const Logo = styled.div` font-weight: bold; font-size: 3.5vh; padding: 1rem; span { color: #f0f0f0; } a { color: black !important; } + div { border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; } ` const MenuList = styled.div` display: flex; justify-content: space-between; .ant-menu-overflow-item.ant-menu-item { position: relative !important; } ` const WebNavBar = (props) => { return ( <> TIMELINE 타임라인 클래스 마이페이지 { props.auth ? <> 로그아웃 : <> 로그인 회원가입 } ) } export default WebNavBar
